{"tid":413900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 其實屋企人好重要","createTime":"2017-09-25T18:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T15:19:53.000Z","uid":110992,"like":742,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa47b880cd439ab798a62694a6d3f1af349992fa","tid":413900,"uid":110992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"話說聽日阿爸要做手術 而個手術可以講係幾重要<br />\n因為一做完就可以知道係好定係壞<br />\n咁重點就係 我好驚係壞阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我真係好中意我爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁講下我同阿爸關係啦<br />\n我阿爸由細到大都算錫我 <br />\n雖然會好惡鬧我打我 但又會暗中幫我 <br />\n所以基本上 我最多嬲佢一日 就嬲完<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n細個我同哥哥好中意打乒乓球<br />\n佢會整張乒乓球台比我<br />\n細個住村屋 有天台 加上阿爸做裝修 好中意自己整野<br />\n<br />\n另外 <br />\nRepeat個年 放jupas個日<br />\n我完全唔敢睇有無大學收我<br />\n我爸同我講<br />\n無大學收 爸爸比錢你去東華讀護士 <br />\n當時東華10萬一年 <br />\n個陣我真係喊左出黎 因為爸爸而句說話 <br />\n好彩 最後都有offer<br />\n<br />\n另外 <br />\n我次次去旅行 <br />\n我爸都好阻止 話驚咩比人呃 <br />\n但次次都提醒我要帶藥<br />\n又幫我買哂所有旅行用既野<br />\n又比錢我去 <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多....<br />\n<br />\n最後 爸爸  我好想同你講<br />\n雖然你次次都叫我早d識男仔 早d結婚 但我知 你唔想個女咁快結 因為我偷聽過你講唔想個女咁快嫁 無人陪你（因為全家得我陪佢傻）<br />\n雖然你好勇敢（扮勇敢） <br />\n但其實我知你好驚做手術 <br />\n因為上次我見到你做手術前喊左出黎 <br />\n但我扮見唔到 因為我驚我喊左出黎 你會仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多謝你 而廿幾年黎 令我無憂無慮 好似小公主咁生活 <br />\n我想做咩 玩咩都比我去做<br />\n我仲記得你經常問我 你以為你做皇帝阿<br />\n我都會答  唔係做皇帝 係做公主<br />\n<br />\n希望而個問題 你個孫／曾孫都可以聽到<br />\n最後最後 你一定會無事嫁 因為我仲要做小公主阿"},{"pid":"e3dc8b881275a0a71c5fbd1bb080599904bc5063","tid":413900,"uid":93855,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"祝你爸爸平安無事"},{"pid":"7844fb4a76c3cd56556f81eb54250aca90631ae0","tid":413900,"uid":89727,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:43:49.000Z","msg":"加油呀 絲打<br />\n爸爸一定會吉人天相架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b0d682b3db6fb7f48ee387f1f2d5a31bb2c3d8","tid":413900,"uid":1339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"d740e03e4d41d26d8541f0595904e2e0a7aa5f78","tid":413900,"uid":29507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:47:29.000Z","msg":"祝你爸爸平安"},{"pid":"4ef95bcb726aa40283123e7863af80e3a7bfde34","tid":413900,"uid":11677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"放心 你老豆實無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cc05b70ab386bc055ee136d77e9a745e39078b","tid":413900,"uid":50029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"加油 爸爸一定無事"},{"pid":"aac49a16f91d6864904fe13947c671201896c3bd","tid":413900,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"標題：其實父幹好重要"},{"pid":"99eac7073495b9fb33b45584246a525b92d189d0","tid":413900,"uid":102009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你爸爸一定無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好羨慕你有咁好既爸爸<br />\n利申 單親家庭長大 跟呀媽住"},{"pid":"9aac03a382faf7a6e5ec500b3b0f921267396c61","tid":413900,"uid":59528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"好羨慕你有個咁好嘅爸爸<br />\n祝你爸爸大步𨈇過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c666f4ef40b279b482b517f9c0266a8ae1becbc","tid":413900,"uid":145769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T18:59:02.000Z","msg":"係我老豆都過左身，無左至親既感覺好怪，唔太真實<br />\n<br />\n希望你爸爸會無事<br />\n之後考順啲"},{"pid":"7bf81da6dfd8d4bf1148d895b7cc733f07a2bf1e","tid":413900,"uid":71173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"一定無事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到我好感動"},{"pid":"1b8fea02d11d42d05da3a8bcdbb555e2f94ea8b7","tid":413900,"uid":82714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:01:25.000Z","msg":"爸爸一定會無事！手術會順順利利"},{"pid":"21e7a9c5669e3c8a56c0a4d01038084ae2ecd54a","tid":413900,"uid":147603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:03:51.000Z","msg":"你爸爸一定會大步纜過架！"},{"pid":"971da72b7996ede019bc223e591550625b0a6f1e","tid":413900,"uid":72486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說聽日阿爸要做手術 而個手術可以講係幾重要<br />\n因為一做完就可以知道係好定係壞<br />\n咁重點就係 我好驚係壞阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我真係好中意我爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁講下我同阿爸關係啦<br />\n我阿爸由細到大都算錫我 <br />\n雖然會好惡鬧我打我 但又會暗中幫我 <br />\n所以基本上 我最多嬲佢一日 就嬲完<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n細個我同哥哥好中意打乒乓球<br />\n佢會整張乒乓球台比我<br />\n細個住村屋 有天台 加上阿爸做裝修 好中意自己整野<br />\n<br />\n另外 <br />\nRepeat個年 放jupas個日<br />\n我完全唔敢睇有無大學收我<br />\n我爸同我講<br />\n無大學收 爸爸比錢你去東華讀護士 <br />\n當時東華10萬一年 <br />\n個陣我真係喊左出黎 因為爸爸而句說話 <br />\n好彩 最後都有offer<br />\n<br />\n另外 <br />\n我次次去旅行 <br />\n我爸都好阻止 話驚咩比人呃 <br />\n但次次都提醒我要帶藥<br />\n又幫我買哂所有旅行用既野<br />\n又比錢我去 <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多....<br />\n<br />\n最後 爸爸  我好想同你講<br />\n雖然你次次都叫我早d識男仔 早d結婚 但我知 你唔想個女咁快結 因為我偷聽過你講唔想個女咁快嫁 無人陪你（因為全家得我陪佢傻）<br />\n雖然你好勇敢（扮勇敢） <br />\n但其實我知你好驚做手術 <br />\n因為上次我見到你做手術前喊左出黎 <br />\n但我扮見唔到 因為我驚我喊左出黎 你會仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多謝你 而廿幾年黎 令我無憂無慮 好似小公主咁生活 <br />\n我想做咩 玩咩都比我去做<br />\n我仲記得你經常問我 你以為你做皇帝阿<br />\n我都會答  唔係做皇帝 係做公主<br />\n<br />\n希望而個問題 你個孫／曾孫都可以聽到<br />\n最後最後 你一定會無事嫁 因為我仲要做小公主阿</blockquote><br />\n陪住爸爸，無事嘅，你既請況我都經歷過"},{"pid":"fa67dd7d680af225e1654ed6590dbc94724c1931","tid":413900,"uid":110992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標題：其實父幹好重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我爸爸係用血汗錢養大我地 做裝修<br />\n供我大學 供我學琴 <br />\n所以我都好尊敬佢<br />\n利申：細個好窮 靠阿爸努力有腦 先慢慢有錢"},{"pid":"8acf740d1af788b63117f8739e7b3b07d60eaae0","tid":413900,"uid":69677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:08:29.000Z","msg":"我為你祈禱,加油!!"},{"pid":"3acf8663df852f3efc6de008cb00d0751172dc8d","tid":413900,"uid":148542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>標題：其實父幹好重要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我爸爸係用血汗錢養大我地 做裝修<br />\n供我大學 供我學琴 <br />\n所以我都好尊敬佢<br />\n利申：細個好窮 靠阿爸努力有腦 先慢慢有錢</blockquote><br />\n利申嗰句同你一樣 <br />\n希望你爸爸會冇事 因為我爸爸都好錫我 好驚佢有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588d44b4ddf47733c20808b419424506b59e631b","tid":413900,"uid":5052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"吉人自有天相 <br />\n樓主你爸爸無事的"},{"pid":"8b9dcc3780b795488aaa20a9f688e77e37c57320","tid":413900,"uid":26003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T19:18:44.000Z","msg":"加油！要信一定會冇事！全連登一齊集氣！"},{"pid":"a565f50d8446cc3eed9b563e4449e03d085939a8","tid":413900,"uid":137847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T20:29:31.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c