"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個同佢關係一般 感情唔係太深 因為佢係好大男人<br />\n好易發脾氣 所以唔係幾會同佢講野 <br />\n直到我出去讀書 <br />\n好記得我臨走前佢係咁講叫我唔好走<br />\n爸爸好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全冇諗過我爸爸會咁樣同我講 <br />\n個一刻真係眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽咪成日都唔中意佢塞錢比我用 話寵壞哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但爸爸佢會特登自己儲起佢啲零用錢<br />\n然後特登去銀行學入數過比我<br />\n真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛你爸爸 要長命百歲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46dcfa8529e27b0aae7f6cd672e7171772b1b882","tid":413900,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"祝早日康復"},{"pid":"35928ce0bde31dfb773cb3c22e90f2f6215d7663","tid":413900,"uid":135227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"加油呀~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好鐘意我爸爸但係唔識表達"},{"pid":"12a1ad2e5a8978515f23ea5ab8369a54a66a22ad","tid":413900,"uid":110992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到我都喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油呀Uncle ! 一定要頂住！<br />\n加油呀絲打 我同我爸既關係都係同你地咁上下  其實做囡既真係會超心痛佢  同超擔心個老豆<br />\n我明 我真係明<br />\n為你打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地都係唔識表達既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d083c797b281a9b416791fa1b062c486ee8c99","tid":413900,"uid":110992,"like":1,"disl